## Detailed Analysis

### 1. Amazon Prime Rewards Visa Signature Card - Best Overall for Online Shopping

**Key specs:**
- Sign-up bonus: $200 Amazon gift card
- Rewards rate: 5% back on Amazon and Whole Foods, 2% on gas/restaurants/drugstores, 1% on everything else
- Annual fee: $0 (requires Amazon Prime membership)
- APR: 18.24%-26.99% variable

**Why it wins:**

5% back at Amazon and Whole Foods — if you already pay for Prime, this is free money on spending you're doing anyway. No annual fee beyond Prime itself. The $200 Amazon gift card sign-up bonus is instant value. The 2% on gas, restaurants, and drugstores is a decent backup rate. The catch: rewards are best redeemed within the Amazon ecosystem.

**Real-world scenario:** Spending $400/month on Amazon

- Monthly rewards: $20.00
- Annual rewards: $240.00
- Annual fee: $0 (Prime membership separate)
- **Net annual value: $240.00**

