### 2. Discover it Cash Back - Best for cashback

**Key specs:**
- Sign-up bonus: Cashback Match: Discover matches all cash back earned first year
- Rewards rate: 5% on rotating categories (up to $1,500/quarter), 1% on everything else
- Annual fee: $0
- APR: 16.24%-27.24% variable

**Why it's competitive:**

The Cashback Match is genuinely incredible for year one — Discover doubles ALL your cashback at the end of the first year. If you hit the 5% rotating categories (which frequently include Amazon, Target, and PayPal quarters), you're effectively earning 10% back for 12 months. After year one, it's a solid 5%/1% card with no annual fee. The trick is remembering to activate each quarter.

**Real-world scenario:** Spending $400/month during 5% online shopping quarters (year one with doubling)

- Quarterly 5% rewards: $60.00
- Doubled at year-end: $120.00
- **Year one total: $240.00** (from online quarters alone)

